<br>
My wife went to that madness (our vaccuum cleaner died, they had a cheap one - I'm unemployed, remember?).  She got there at 15 minutes to and the line was huge.  But this one had it pretty straightened out.  They had carts lined up on the outside for everyone so basically people had to form a line and they let people in controlled and not just 'on your mark, get set...'.<br>
<br>
The line was so long that people were already walking out with their stuff before my wife got in.  And of course the vaccuum cleaner was gone.  But she got a slightly more expensive one that probably was better anyway. <p>“How can you claim to love a God you can’t see if you fail to love the brother or sister standing right in front of you?” – Mother Theresa</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsparrowshearth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mallaidh08>Mallaidh08</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=green><b>Caustic Court Jester,<br>Kind Confessor</b></font></span><br>  Posts: 53<br> <font color=#B87333>(11/30/03 9:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsparrowshearthfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=198.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/pi_nervous.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Woman Knocked Unconscious While Shopping</span><hr size=1> I refuse to step foot outside the house on &quot;Black Friday&quot; before noon.  That's because not only are people insane about shopping, they can't drive, either.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   IHOP opened at 4:00 AM on Friday, but thankfully enough I didn't have to be there because I was gone!!!!!  And that poor lady... I bet she thinks twice before she steps in front of greedy mobs.  I would, at least. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsparrowshearth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wordwolf>WordWolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style=color:green;><b>Sir WordWolf,<br>Keeper of Odd Knowledge,<br>Bachelor-at-Arms</b></span></span><br>  Posts: 136<br> 